title: Newly Renovated 3 Bed/3 Bath - Panoramic Views - Luxury Amenities !!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
